    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-808a-8cb9-ff0ba11f6659",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The first-to-second year in an undergraduate program is among the most important stages of a student’s academic career (especially when it comes to deciding whether to drop out or not). Authors analyze the factors behind dropout in Italy at two-levels of resolution:",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-808a-8cb9-ff0ba11f6659",
        "parent": {
